  "description": "Fix Gallery Card Display Issues\n\nResolve layout and content rendering problems in the gallery-card component where blank space appears at the bottom and the title is not visible.\n\nRequirements:\n- Locate the gallery-card component in the codebase\n- Fix the missing title display (ensure title text is being rendered and is visible)\n- Remove or correct the blank space appearing at the bottom of the card\n- Verify proper spacing and alignment of all card elements\n- Check CSS/styling for layout issues (flexbox, grid, padding, margins, height calculations)\n- Ensure the card displays correctly across different screen sizes\n- Test with various content lengths (short titles, long titles, missing titles)\n\nEdge cases to consider:\n- Cards with no title data\n- Cards with very long titles\n- Different image aspect ratios that may affect layout\n- Container constraints that may cause spacing issues",
